WEBVTT

00:00:07.017 --> 00:00:09.957
Sitting around a campfire, 
you can feel its heat,

00:00:09.957 --> 00:00:13.167
smell the woody smoke, 
and hear it crackle.

00:00:13.167 --> 00:00:14.437
If you get too close,

00:00:14.437 --> 00:00:17.107
it burns your eyes 
and stings your nostrils.

00:00:17.107 --> 00:00:19.678
You could stare at the bright
flames forever

00:00:19.678 --> 00:00:23.728
as they twist and flicker 
in endless incarnations.

00:00:23.728 --> 00:00:25.938
But what exactly are you looking at?

00:00:25.938 --> 00:00:28.558
The flames are obviously not solid,

00:00:28.558 --> 00:00:29.978
nor are they liquid.

